{"tid":199251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又多個柒頭亂過馬路比車撞","createTime":"2017-04-13T05:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T11:09:48.000Z","uid":51620,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43cb4e8060f926b541386abc3edd65f1cda74e4b","tid":199251,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170413/bkn-20170413101219319-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170413%2Fbkn-20170413101219319-0413_00822_001.html&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5a91433b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170413/bkn-20170413101219319-0413_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣發生救護電單車撞途人意外，早上8時許，一輛救護電單車，駛經沙咀道福來邨對開時，一名女子突橫過馬路，救護電單車收掣不及將其撞倒，女事主遭撞飛，拋離10外米墮地撞傷頭部昏迷，其他駕駛人士見狀報案，救護車到場將傷者送院治理。現場消息稱，當時救護車開着警號，警方正對意外展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n女傷者住祈德尊新邨，其子女近日趁復活節假期去了歐洲旅行。事後其五名親友，包括教會的友人接獲消息趕到醫院了解。據悉，女傷者骨折，經搶救後已恢復知覺，需要留醫深切治療部。消防處派員到醫院向家屬慰問，及了解傷者情況。"},{"pid":"41bf0741509f69cdd340e9e0cf8c5e5328f36140","tid":199251,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611348a4d2170d036a7466c4a6ec81a289094bb6","tid":199251,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"睇清楚年齡同樣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24642d48e7f634ea4f8d348de1e2198f5e982b1c","tid":199251,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"無死到係咪唔使積口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241a9f5e41c1e32fc0a7f1cf220dfe475f8b2448","tid":199251,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"都味死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":